e","package-manager",false,true,"","lockfile","lockfile 是一种用于记录依赖的版本信息的文件","/_workflow/package-manager/lockfile.md",{"type":183,"children":184,"toc":225},"root",[185,194,200,206,211],{"type":186,"tag":187,"props":188,"children":190},"element","h4",{"id":189},"为什么用了-lockfile-还是不能保证环境统一",[191],{"type":192,"value":193},"text","为什么用了 lockfile 还是不能保证环境统一？",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":196,"children":197},"p",{},[198],{"type":192,"value":199},"因为 npm install 时可能会根据 Semver 自动更新依赖的版本。Semver 被设计用来解决模块不同版本的兼容性问题，但是并不完美，因为在实际的代码开发中，所有代码更改都没用绝对的 no breaking change 一说。也就是说，尽管是小版本改动，也可能带来问题。",{"type":186,"tag":187,"props":201,"children":203},{"id":202},"lockfile-vs-shrinkwrap",[204],{"type":192,"value":205},"lockfile vs shrinkwrap？",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":207,"children":208},{},[209],{"type":192,"value":210},"npm 的 lockfile 设计用于开发环境锁定依赖版本，而 shrinkwrap 包含依赖树的版本记录，所以更适合用于生产环境。",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":212,"children":213},{},[214,216],{"type":192,"value":215},"相关：",{"type":186,"tag":217,"props":218,"children":222},"a",{"href":219,"rel":220},"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/22934066",[221],"nofollow",[223],{"type":192,"value":224},"为什么我不使用 shrinkwrap（lock）",{"title":178,"searchDepth":226,"depth":226,"links":227},2,[],"markdown","content:6.maps:_workflow:package-manager:lockfile.md","content","6.maps/_workflow/package-manager/lockfile.md","6.maps/_workflow/package-manager/lockfile","md",[235,239],{"_path":236,"title":237,"description":238},"/maps/_workflow/package-manager","包管理器","用于管理项目依赖的工具",{"_path":240,"title":241,"description":242},"/maps/_workflow/package-manager/npm","NPM","NPM 包管理器完整指南，包含 package.json 配置、镜像源管理、依赖安装等核心功能的详细说明。",1772185472150]